social_posts.post_text:
i wouldn’t be where i am today without this woman. you created the most special space for kids where we can call it home, you truly bring out the best in every dancer, and inspire so many around the world. all i wanted to do was be at the studio with you 24/7 because you made me love dance that much. i miss our rehearsals together and you screaming at the top of your lungs lol 
there’s not enough words to explain how much i love you and how much you mean to me but i hope you have the most amazing day today! 
HAPPY BIRTHDAY
